                        <h4>Facts about the Mirak Nursery:</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Varieties of trees grown – ash, pine, wild apple, wild pear, oak beech</li>
                            <li>Over 1,000kg (2,200lbs) of seeds sown annually</li>
                            <li>A new pipeline installed provided water to the nursery and 32 village families</li>
                            <li>All 90 hectares of land secured in Tashir were planted with Mirak seedlings in 2016-2017</li>
                            <li>A new greenhouse provides higher survival rate for other types of seedlings to be planted throughout the other regions of Armenia. </li>
                        </ul>
